snippet.title: Srdjan Susnic
snippet.description:
This channel is all about my own tutorials on making games, using artificial intelligence and implementing machine learning algorithms.

Besides demos of my own games, here you'll find helpful tutorials that show you how to create AI bots that can learn to play a variety of games.

For example, you can learn how to use genetic algorithms and artificial neural networks to perfectly play Flappy Bird game. Or how to make your own Quick Draw game by performing image classification based on convolutional neural networks.

The games are written in Javascript using Phaser framework and TensorFlow for machine learning.

All tutorials include free source code. 

If this sounds interesting to you, make sure to subscribe and click the notification bell so you never miss a new video!

To learn more, visit my official website and read articles here:
https://www.askforgametask.com
